ces, including treatment for Retina, Cataract, Glaucoma, and more.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-a615f0a112dce6be6 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_a615f0a112dce6be6\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"a615f0a112dce6be6\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#a615f0a112dce6be6\" href=\"#a615f0a112dce6be6\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">Is Giridhar Eye Institute NABH accredited?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"a615f0a112dce6be6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_a615f0a112dce6be6\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Yes, Giridhar Eye Institute is an NABH accredited eye hospital known for its high standards in patient care.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-5f070cb85349bc2e3 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_5f070cb85349bc2e3\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"5f070cb85349bc2e3\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#5f070cb85349bc2e3\" href=\"#5f070cb85349bc2e3\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">How can I book an appointment at Giridhar Eye Institute?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"5f070cb85349bc2e3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_5f070cb85349bc2e3\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>You can book an appointment online through our website or by contacting our front desk directly.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-792de12c046efb6a1 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_792de12c046efb6a1\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"792de12c046efb6a1\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#792de12c046efb6a1\" href=\"#792de12c046efb6a1\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What is the cost of a standard eye consultation?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"792de12c046efb6a1\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_792de12c046efb6a1\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>The cost may vary based on the consultation type. Please contact our team for specific details.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-04bb8ad8f09e8053c fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_04bb8ad8f09e8053c\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"04bb8ad8f09e8053c\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#04bb8ad8f09e8053c\" href=\"#04bb8ad8f09e8053c\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">Do you offer specialized care for children\u2019s eye conditions? <\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"04bb8ad8f09e8053c\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_04bb8ad8f09e8053c\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Yes, we have a dedicated Pediatric Ophthalmology department specializing in the diagnosis and treatment of children&#8217;s eye conditions.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-70d53dddc17c10738 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_70d53dddc17c10738\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"70d53dddc17c10738\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#70d53dddc17c10738\" href=\"#70d53dddc17c10738\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What is the Medical Retina Fellowship program?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"70d53dddc17c10738\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_70d53dddc17c10738\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Our Medical Retina Fellowship offers advanced training for ophthalmologists in diagnosing and treating retinal diseases.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-1e9dd337aadfa01f2 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_1e9dd337aadfa01f2\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"1e9dd337aadfa01f2\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#1e9dd337aadfa01f2\" href=\"#1e9dd337aadfa01f2\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">Do you provide free surgeries or camps for the underprivileged?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"1e9dd337aadfa01f2\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_1e9dd337aadfa01f2\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>Yes, through our community outreach programs, we offer free surgeries and conduct eye care camps every year.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-d44d5e390bfd91707 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_d44d5e390bfd91707\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"d44d5e390bfd91707\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#d44d5e390bfd91707\" href=\"#d44d5e390bfd91707\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">How do I donate to support your eye care programs?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"d44d5e390bfd91707\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_d44d5e390bfd91707\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>You can make a donation through our &#8220;Make a Donation&#8221; page to help us restore sight and prevent blindness.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-176d8721b787002c6 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_176d8721b787002c6\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"176d8721b787002c6\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#176d8721b787002c6\" href=\"#176d8721b787002c6\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What is the duration of the DNB program in Ophthalmology?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"176d8721b787002c6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_176d8721b787002c6\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>The DNB program is a prestigious postgraduate medical qualification that typically spans 3 years.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-panel panel-default panel-82827d34b2a11adee fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode\" style=\"--awb-content-font-size:20px;--awb-content-font-family:&quot;Mulish&quot;;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-family:&quot;Kumbh Sans&quot;;--awb-title-font-weight:500;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-title-font-size:22px;--awb-title-color:var(--awb-color8);\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 class=\"panel-title toggle\" id=\"toggle_82827d34b2a11adee\"><a aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"82827d34b2a11adee\" role=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion-1797-1\" data-target=\"#82827d34b2a11adee\" href=\"#82827d34b2a11adee\"><span class=\"fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"fa-fusion-box active-icon fa-minus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><i class=\"fa-fusion-box inactive-icon fa-plus fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"fusion-toggle-heading\">What safety protocols are in place during eye surgeries?<\/span><\/a><\/h4><\/div><div id=\"82827d34b2a11adee\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \" aria-labelledby=\"toggle_82827d34b2a11adee\"><div class=\"panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix\">\n<p>We follow strict NABH guidelines, ensuring the highest standards of hygiene and safety during all surgeries.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"100-width.php","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"_uf_show_specific_survey":0,"_uf_disable_surveys":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1797","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1797","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1797"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1797\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8982,"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1797\/revisions\/8982"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1797"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}